annotationA: 40S ribosomal protein S11; Structural constituent of ribosome. It is involved in the biological process described with: mitotic spindle elongation; translation; mitotic spindle organization; neurogenesis; Belongs to the universal ribosomal protein uS17 family
annotationB: 60S acidic ribosomal protein P2; Plays an important role in the elongation step of protein synthesis
